    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1260923001621319680",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范》，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年7月15日- 2025年7月21日，规则预计于2025年7月22日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：1、全文规则表述简化，详细内容通过细则对规则进行补充说明；2、部分违禁场景表述调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px;\">原规则链接：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2495&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2495&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">修订后全文如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241927157672972288&amp;btype=1\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">危害国家安全、破坏政治稳定与社会稳定的有害信息类</span></strong></a></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.1</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">含有反动、破坏国家统一的商品及信息、破坏主权及领土完整、破坏社会稳定、涉及国家机密、扰乱社会秩序的商品及信息</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">宣扬恐怖主义、宗教极端思想、民族仇恨等的商品及信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">发布任何歪曲历史，美化他国侵略史实或宣扬军国主义思想，或伤害中国人民和中华民族感情的商品及信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未在境内出版发行或已停止发行销售的涉政书刊及收藏性的涉密书籍、音像制品、视频、文件资料、<span style=\"background: yellow;\">游戏</span>以及特殊邮票</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规发布国家机关用品或不当营销的商品及信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.6</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">未经授权的含有国家领导人相关的商品或信息</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">涉国家领导人关联的书籍、培训资料、教材等其他出版物，领导人姓名或职务错写、漏写、<span style=\"background: yellow;\">遮挡</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.1.8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&ldquo;问题地图&rdquo;及衍生品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">1.1.9</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">违反《互联网宗教服务管理规定》相关管理规定，带有非法宗教、邪教、种族、性别、地域、职业歧视的相关商品或信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">1.1.10</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">为完成党政工作提供违规服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.2</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241923649624215552&amp;btype=1\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">武器、仿真枪、管制器具类</span></strong></a></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.2.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">枪支、弹药、军火</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.2.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">枪支、弹药、军火的相关器材、配件、仿制品及其制作方法</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.2.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">管制类刀具等管制器具</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.2.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">其他可能用于危害他人人身安全的管制器具</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">毒品及毒品吸食工具类： </span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.3.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">毒品、制毒原料、制毒化学品及致瘾性药物</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.3.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">毒品吸食工具、配件及介绍制作毒品的相关方法及信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.3.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">带有毒品相关表述的内容</span><span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.4</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241926361707319296&amp;btype=1\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">军警用品类</span></strong></a></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.4.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">军用、警用制服标志及配件</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.4.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">军警设备及制品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.4.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">禁止借军警名义营销</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.4.4&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">严禁出售退役报废机动车</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">危险化学品及易燃易爆品类：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.5.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">国家禁止出售的危险化学品、剧毒化学品、易制爆化学品等</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.5.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">易燃、易爆物品，以及介绍制作易燃易爆品方法的相关教程、书籍</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.5.3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">农业部发布的禁用限用类农药</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">1.5.4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">放射性物质及射线装置</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.6</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1234418796756865024&amp;btype=1\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">色情低俗、暴力内容及催情用品类</span></strong></a></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.6.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">含有色情淫秽内容的音像制品及视频；色情陪聊服务、成人网站论坛的账号/邀请码及其他淫秽物品及信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.6.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">用于传播色情信息的软件、种子文件、网盘资源及图片；含有情色、暴力、低俗内容的图片、音像制品及视频；原味内衣及相关产品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.6.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">可致使他人暂时失去反抗能力、意识模糊的口服或外用的催情类商品，以及人造处女膜</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.6.4</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;\">含有暴力、低俗内容的文字、图片及信息</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"_Hlk152581233\"></a><a name=\"_Hlk152581144\"></a><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241927792086618112&amp;btype=1\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">危害未成年人身心健康类</span></strong></a></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未成年人色情低俗类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未成年人邪典类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未成年人宗教类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未成年人欺凌类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未成年人其他违法导向类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">引导未成年人犯罪类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.7.7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">未成年人不良信息</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.8</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">侵犯他人及企业隐私、信息安全类：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.8.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">盗取或破解账号密码的软件、工具、教程及产物</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.8.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">用于非法摄像、录音、取证等用途的设备</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.8.3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">个人隐私信息及企业内部数据；提供隐私信息查询服务等</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9</span></strong><span style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">医药类</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">疫苗、血液制品、麻醉药品、精神药品、医疗用毒性药品、放射性药品、易制毒药品、蛋白同化制剂、肽类激素（胰岛素除外）、终止妊娠药品、戒毒药品、医疗机构制剂等国家实行特殊管理的药品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">我国法律法规规定的其它药品零售企业不得经营的药品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">根据国家法律法规或京东治理要求，京东认定的高风险及高警示的禁止销售的其他药品（含跨境药品等）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">美白针剂、溶脂针剂、填充针剂、瘦身针剂等用于人体注射的注射类商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">相关法律法规规定的禁止网络销售的医疗器械</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.9.6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">监管部门公示查处的兽药；兽药监督管理部门禁止生产、使用、销售的兽药</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.10</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">人类器官及动植物，动物捕杀工具类： </span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">人体器官、遗体</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">人类遗传资源材料和人类遗传资源信息</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">国家重点保护类动物、濒危动物的活体、内脏、任何肢体、皮毛、标本或其他制成品，已灭绝动物与现有国家二级以上保护动物的化石</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">国家保护的有益的或者有重要经济、科学研究价值的陆生野生动物的活体、内脏、任何肢体、皮毛、标本或其他制成品</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">国家保护类植物活体（树苗除外）</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">严重危害动物安全的动物捕杀设备及配件</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">猫狗肉、猫狗皮毛、鱼翅、熊胆及其制品等其他有违公益或对当地生态系统可能造成重大破坏的生物物种及其制品</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">1.10.8</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">病原微生物</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">违反国家行政法规禁止销售的商品及服务</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.11.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">涉嫌违反《中华人民共和国文物保护法》等相关规定的文物<strong>：</strong>明出土地和出土时间的文物，如1969年出土于甘肃省某墓中的马踏飞燕等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.11.2</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241929979575537664&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">烟草专卖品、烟草专用机械、电子烟及相关配件</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.11.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">企业公章等</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.11.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">涉及网络账号类买卖服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.11.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">其他国家相关法规禁止发布或存在风险的商品及服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">涉及走私、盗窃、抢劫、欺诈、作弊、赌博等非法所得及非法用途类： </span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">伪造变造国家机关或特定机构颁发的文件、证书、公章、防伪标签等，提供仅限国家机关或特定机构方可提供的服务</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; color: black;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">考试答案、作弊工具及服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">为完成学术研究、学业任务等提供违规服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">涉嫌欺诈的软件、工具及服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">涉嫌盗窃等非法用途软件、工具及服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">炒作博客人气、炒作网站人气、自动刷屏软件、 代投票类商品或信息</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; color: black;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">赌博博彩类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.12.8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">尚可使用或用于报销的票据（及服务）,尚可使用的外贸单证以及代理报关、清单、商检、单证手续的服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.13</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">通讯、上网、无线电类设备类：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.13.1</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241924296490749952&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">破网、翻墙软件及VPN</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">代理服务</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.13.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">卫星信号收发装置及软件；用于无线电信号屏蔽的仪器或设备</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.13.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">已激活的手机卡、上网卡等违反国家规定的商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.14</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">货币金融相关商品及服务：</span></strong><span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.14.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">伪造变造的货币以及印制设备</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.14.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">正在流通的人民币、仿制人民币及与人民币相关的商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.14.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">流通中的外币及相关外币汇兑服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.14.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">基于区块链技术生成的虚拟货币等数字化产品及衍生服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.14.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">金融相关产品及相关服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.15</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">交通、航空设备及相关服务：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.15.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">可能用于逃避交通管理的商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.15.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">具有交通安全隐患的机动车配件或其他改装设备类商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.15.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规代办机动车服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.15.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">载人航空器、航空配件、模型图纸类商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">1.16</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">封建迷信相关商品及服务：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.16.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: yellow;\">算命、超度、风水、做法事、人骨法器等封建迷信类商品及服务</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.17</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违背公序良俗相关商品及服务</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.17.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违背公序良俗类</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.18</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">游戏及虚拟类：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.18.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">外挂、私服相关的网游类商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.18.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">无法即时到账或存在其他交付风险的虚拟类商品</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.19</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">应急性禁售类：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.19.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">应对重大突发舆情、监管事件，临时禁售的品类，如315曝光、监管部门执法曝光、监管预警通报等</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">应对重大突发舆情、监管事件、临时禁售的品类商品或信息。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">商家不得通过任何方式规避本规范及其他京东开放平台禁售商品的相关管控措施，商家不得在包括但不限于京东商品页面（包括但不限于商品标题、商品描述、商品图片），店铺页面（包括但不限于店铺命名、店铺分类、店铺介绍、店铺公告、店铺留言），以及在线客服对话页面、社区和论坛等信息发布区块发布禁售商品相关信息；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">如果商家利用平台监管漏洞持续销售违法违规商品，或通过模糊商品描述、使用&ldquo;马赛克&rdquo;遮挡关键标识、在客服环节引流销售、拆分关键词等方式故意规避平台审核，平台将从严处理，并有权将相关违法违规线索上报主管部门；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有约定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无约定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.4</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">如商家违反法律法规、监管政策或本规范的，京东有权依据法律法规、协议、《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》以及本规范等对于该违规行为进行包括但不限于下架商品、<span style=\"background: white;\">扣除违约金、违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、限制发布商品，店铺屏蔽、</span>限制提报及投放营销活动、全店下架、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">附则：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">京东可根据运营情况随时调整本规则并以公告的形式向商家公示；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">本规则于2025年7月15日修订，于2025年7月22日生效。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>",
